<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Parts & Compatibility — ISRM</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles.css">
  <style>
    .page-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--surface) 60%, var(--bg-dark) 100%);
      padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .page-hero::before {
      content: "🔩";
      position: absolute;
      right: 6%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 9rem;
      opacity: 0.07;
      pointer-events: none;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .page-hero-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary), var(--accent));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .page-hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .page-hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; }
    .hero-stat-number { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); line-height: 1; }
    .hero-stat-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .parts-controls {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .parts-controls input,
    .parts-controls select {
      padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .parts-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .parts-table thead {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1), rgba(0, 164, 204, 0.1));
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    }

    .parts-table th {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .parts-table td {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    .parts-table tr:hover {
      background: var(--surface-2);
    }

    .parts-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .part-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .compatibility-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .compat-yes {
      background: rgba(6, 167, 125, 0.2);
      color: var(--success);
    }

    .compat-partial {
      background: rgba(245, 166, 35, 0.2);
      color: var(--warning);
    }

    .compat-no {
      background: rgba(214, 48, 49, 0.2);
      color: var(--danger);
    }

    .part-categories {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .part-category {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }

    .part-category:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .part-category-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .part-category h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .parts-table {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .parts-table th,
      .parts-table td {
        padding: 0.8rem;
      }

      .parts-controls {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .parts-controls input,
      .parts-controls select {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
    <div class="nav-container">
      
        <a href="../index.html" class="nav-brand">
          <span class="brand-icon">⚙️</span>
          <span class="brand-text">ISRM</span>
        </a>

      <ul class="nav-menu" id="navMenu">
        <li><a href="../repair-guides/index.html" class="nav-link">Guides</a></li>
        <li><a href="../diagnostics/index.html" class="nav-link">Diagnostics</a></li>
        <li><a href="../parts/index.html" class="nav-link active">Parts</a></li>
        <li><a href="../models/index.html" class="nav-link">Models</a></li>
        <li><a href="../community/index.html" class="nav-link">Community</a></li>
      </ul>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle">☰</button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="breadcrumb" style="padding: 0 0 1rem; margin: 0;">
        <a href="../index.html">ISRM Home</a><span>›</span>Parts &amp; Compatibility
      </div>
      <h1>Parts &amp; Compatibility</h1>
      <p>Find and verify compatible parts for GY6-platform and Vespa/Piaggio scooters. Compatibility tables sourced from official specifications.</p>
      <div class="page-hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-number">GY6</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Platform</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-number">Vespa</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Piaggio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-number">4</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Categories</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-number">Free</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Always</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="container" style="padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <div class="parts-controls">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Search parts..." id="partSearch" style="flex: 1;" />
      <select id="modelFilter" style="min-width: 200px;">
        <option value="">All Models</option>
        <option value="gy6">GY6 Scooters</option>
        <option value="vespa">Vespa Models</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary);">Engine Parts</h2>
    <table class="parts-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Part Name</th>
          <th>GY6 (139QMB)</th>
          <th>Vespa Primavera</th>
          <th>Vespa ZIP</th>
          <th>Notes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Spark Plug</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-partial">NGK CR8E</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td>Check gap before installation</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Air Filter</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td>Model-specific cartridge required</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Oil Filter</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td>HF556 standard for GY6</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Piston Kit</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-partial">Check Size</span></td>
          <td>Size varies by engine code</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 3rem;">Transmission Parts</h2>
    <table class="parts-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Part Name</th>
          <th>GY6 (139QMB)</th>
          <th>Vespa Primavera</th>
          <th>Vespa ZIP</th>
          <th>Notes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">CVT Belt</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td>750x16 standard width</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Variator Rollers</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-no">Different</span></td>
          <td>Weight depends on performance goal</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="part-name">Clutch Belt</td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-partial">Drive Belt</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td><span class="compatibility-badge compat-yes">Compatible</span></td>
          <td>Primary drive system</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 3rem;">Browse by Category</h2>
    <div class="part-categories">
      <div class="part-category">
        <div class="part-category-icon">🔧</div>
        <h3>Engine Parts</h3>
        <p>Pistons, rings, gaskets, seals</p>
      </div>
      <div class="part-category">
        <div class="part-category-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h3>Transmission</h3>
        <p>Belt, rollers, variator</p>
      </div>
      <div class="part-category">
        <div class="part-category-icon">🔩</div>
        <h3>Fasteners</h3>
        <p>Bolts, nuts, washers</p>
      </div>
      <div class="part-category">
        <div class="part-category-icon">🛢️</div>
        <h3>Fluids</h3>
        <p>Oil, coolant, brake fluid</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
